15
00:01:26,220 --> 00:01:27,060
Why should I?

16
00:01:27,700 --> 00:01:28,620
All these years,

17
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:30,860
you've found nothing.

18
00:01:31,460 --> 00:01:32,780
Should I fear his search?

19
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:35,020
You're right, Bro.

20
00:01:35,620 --> 00:01:37,060
When did I ever dare to check on you?

21
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:39,100
Well,

22
00:01:39,980 --> 00:01:40,820
you didn't do it.

23
00:01:41,620 --> 00:01:42,980
What about your men?

24
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:47,520
Just kidding.

25
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:48,380
I was kidding, Bro.

26
00:01:49,180 --> 00:01:50,460
Gotta go.

27
00:01:56,860 --> 00:01:57,700
Mr. Li,

28
00:01:57,940 --> 00:01:58,877
if you leave me alone,

29
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,380
I'll make a deal with you.

30
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:01,580
Let's hear it.

31
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:03,460
Zhang Chongguang is involved

32
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:06,420
in Xia Dashui's injury.

33
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:09,060
Are you sure?

34
00:02:16,970 --> 00:02:18,217
Dad, you wanted to see me?

35
00:02:21,620 --> 00:02:22,460
Old man,

36
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:25,220
