40
00:02:31,500 --> 00:02:33,140
You don't know

41
00:02:33,140 --> 00:02:34,260
what your men are doing?

42
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,180
The one who wants to kill me

43
00:02:41,220 --> 00:02:42,380
might be you.

44
00:02:56,860 --> 00:02:58,060
It's not the weekend.

45
00:02:59,100 --> 00:02:59,940
No one's here?

46
00:03:07,020 --> 00:03:07,860
Zhang Chongguang.

47
00:03:08,460 --> 00:03:09,300
Zhang Chongguang.

48
