57
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:33,270
On behalf of the company, thank you.

58
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:37,340
Do you know the workers are innocent?

59
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:39,220
Yes, they are.

60
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:42,300
But the team contracts with the head office.

61
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:45,140
The head office gets to decide.

62
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:46,940
Oh, I see.

63
00:03:47,540 --> 00:03:49,140
You used to work at construction sites,

64
00:03:49,420 --> 00:03:50,300
doing hard labor.

65
00:03:51,020 --> 00:03:52,460
Anything that requires some thinking

66
