67
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:03,660
Old man,

68
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:06,140
why is Zhang Chongguang overseeing the site?

69
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,980
How could you change workers

70
00:04:09,460 --> 00:04:10,340
as you please?

71
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:14,220
(Pawn)

72
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:15,980
Old man,

73
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:16,980
