76
00:04:21,780 --> 00:04:22,620
How about that?

77
00:04:22,940 --> 00:04:26,060
Do you want to be a rule-maker
just like me?

78
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:41,460
Secretary Wu?

79
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,180
Why are you here?

80
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:46,100
Remember this pawn?

81
00:04:46,420 --> 00:04:47,820
(Pawn)

82
