86
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:59,420
There's one thing I can't figure out.

87
00:05:00,260 --> 00:05:01,380
Tell me,

88
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:03,660
do the rich

89
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,100
really get to do

90
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:07,780
whatever they want?

91
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:10,740
To avoid changing equip,

92
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:13,300
